5. Directory Layout
-------------------

    5.1 TaliesinPHP(tm) - Typical App Directory Structure
    -----------------------------------------------------
    note: I used the "Conventional Modular" directory layout that Zend prefers.
          This is a clean layout, and works really well with the MVC pattern.

    /appname
        /app
            /config (global, optional)
            /(module 1)
                /config (module specific, optional as needed)
                /controllers
                /models
                /views
            /(module 2)
                /controllers
                /models
                /views
            /(module n)
                /controllers
                /models
                /views
        /docroot
            /assets
                /images
                /js
                /css
            index.php
        /lib
            /taliesin
            /extlib
                /(3rd party libs)
        /var
            /tmp
                /sessions
                /cache
            /logs
            /cron

